Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:04.26,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still wondering why I have to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.26,0:00:06.49,Flashback_Italics,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:08.66,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to regret the way I lived!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:13.74,Flashback_Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you going to do when someone \Nyou saved kills someone else in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:17.37,Flashback_Italics,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,When you die, you should \Nbe surrounded by people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:21.10,Flashback_Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,It's been decided that you'll \Nbe secretly executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:24.52,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided how I'm going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:30.92,Flashback_Italics,Yoshino,0000,0000,0000,,That would mean people cursed me \Nand my mom with those hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:32.76,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,What is a proper death?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:36.65,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,The value of life would become ambiguous...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:40.21,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't even understand the importance \Nof those I care about anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.78,0:00:42.27,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,And that scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:45.26,Flashback_Italics,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:48.70,Flashback_Italics,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,When you die, you should \Nbe surrounded by people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:50.71,Flashback_Italics,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,Help others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:53.03,Flashback_Italics,Yuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I can't afford to die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:58.86,Flashback_Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,So I've never once regretted saving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.86,0:01:01.26,Flashback_Italics,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,We're accomplices.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:02.62,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.21,0:01:04.26,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,lose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:07.04,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:08.69,Flashback_Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:10.81,Flashback_Italics,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,to my brothers in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:13.06,Flashback_Italics,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strong kid, so help others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:16.03,Flashback_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready to witness it, Itadori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:18.64,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,People die. There's no stopping that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:21.24,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted them to at \Nleast have proper deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:26.00,Flashback_Italics,Yaga,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to blame your grandfather \Nwhen you're killed by a curse, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:29.91,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,...and have lots of them \Nwatching over me when I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:33.76,Flashback_Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,But tears were shed over \Nthe lives I ended tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:36.74,Flashback_Italics,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,People are going to die because you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.99,Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&}Episode 42\N{\fs30\fscy150}Right and Wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:59.07,Show_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,825)\pos(320,10)\3c&H8ECEDD&}JUJUTSU KAISEN\N{\fs16\bord0\fscy100\c&HDEDCE0&}Shibuya Incident
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:56.03,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Malaysia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.24,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.07,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Malaysia...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.32,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Kuantan would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:07.17,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll build a home on a secluded beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:11.30,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I already have a mountain of books \Nthat I've bought and never touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.00,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll read through them page by page,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:17.99,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,like I'm taking back all the time I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.39,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:24.38,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm going to save Fushiguro-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.73,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,And Maki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.84,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What about Naobito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.04,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.12,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.89,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Exhausted, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.61,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.27,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I've already done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:11.87,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.70,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here. The whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.41,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:32.63,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here. The whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:35.00,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we chat for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.63,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,You and I have gone at it \Na few times, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:52.07,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Haibara, what was I even hoping \Nto accomplish in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.64,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:59.10,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I ran away, and yet I came back over \Nsome vague reason like a job worth doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.21,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.83,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:20.40,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't, Haibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.78,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.75,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just become a curse upon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:33.88,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.82,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.20,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I sh—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.85,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Itadori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.61,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:48.19,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.30,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:11:00.01,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you, Mahito?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:03.37,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to shout! I can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.88,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Yuji Itadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.54,Main,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.86,Main,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.42,Main,Human,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.42,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Multiplicity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.09,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Body Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:17.65,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,If only I'd used a little more force,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.04,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I could've stabbed through your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:26.88,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,How can you possibly
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.16,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,toy with countless
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:32.73,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,people's lives over and over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:41.94,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be satisfied if I counted each \None off my fingers with a look of regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.27,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start doing that with the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:49.80,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll grant you a simple answer \Nsince you're such a simple guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.60,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Yuji Itadori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.64,Main,Junpei,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.49,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,You are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:05.02,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:07.31,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Quit snapping at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.43,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a curse's nonsense, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.54,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.99,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,until you're willing to accept that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.45,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,you can't beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.69,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,On and on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.88,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,You talk a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:29.35,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Those your dying words?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.30,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:38.18,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin would never make the \Nmistake of losing himself to anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.85,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.46,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.46,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:47.67,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...a jujutsu sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.00,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Nice. Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:52.01,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Time for round two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:57.03,Show_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\1c&H213835&\3c&H75EFED&\blur20\1a&HE0&\3a&HC0&\pos(320,18)}JUJUTSU KAISEN
