Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:13.56,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.11,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,If I pick the wrong moments \Nto take risks, I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:20.24,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll attack mostly with\Ntransfigured humans for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.78,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.29,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,He has even more tricks than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.34,Main,YouthA,0000,0000,0000,,A kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.34,Main,YouthB,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:39.04,Main,YouthB,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous and full of \Nmonsters over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.04,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.38,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.11,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:49.06,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,There's no safe place in Shibuya right now, \Nso get as far away as you—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:54.06,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:04.79,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:05.74,Main,YouthA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:09.76,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure your imagination isn't stunted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:10.75,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:12.51,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.40,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,That all depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:18.72,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,This is the most effective tool \Nagainst Itadori's mental state.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.20,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:24.76,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,We have one more card for insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:26.12,Flashback,People,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.22,Flashback,People,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.52,Flashback,People,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.80,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, drink, drink, drink them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.23,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Drink, drink, drink them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.72,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Drink, drink, drink them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:34.92,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Drink away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:40.80,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,959)\an1\fnArial\bord1.5\3a&HE0&\blur1\shad0\b1\fs26\pos(30,310)}21:30        Shibuya Station, B4F
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.14,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.22,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I have plenty stocked up already,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.90,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}so you can do whatever you want \Nwith the people on floor B5.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:46.05,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time to recommence \Nthe "Let's Kill Itadori" show!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:47.63,Flashback,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,Burp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:48.63,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:50.04,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Jogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:52.32,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:53.80,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:56.55,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.98,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,You wander around the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:01.13,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Just come back when I call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.69,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You don't have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:05.26,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:07.76,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\frz17.46\pos(472,230)\bord3\shad0\c&H3F4845&\3c&H454E49&}He split\Ninto two!!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.14,0:20:07.76,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\frz17.46\pos(472,230)\shad0\c&H3F4845&\3c&HF4F7F4&}He split\Ninto two!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.85,Sign_Basic,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8B918E&\3c&HF3FAF2&\shad0\frz281.3\pos(74,120)}Bye-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.77,Flashback,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:13.02,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Boing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.02,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(209,1)\pos(385,150)\frz8\fs18\bord2\shad0\c&H24291B&\3c&HD9DCD2&}Boing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:17.19,Flashback,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,He got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.86,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:32.87,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnArial\bord1.5\3a&HE0&\blur1\shad0\b1\fs26\pos(348,310)}23:16        {\fs20}Dogenzaka Alleys
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.75,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did you see that earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.40,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That was crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:32.52,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I was just wandering around \Nthat area not long ago, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.79,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Patch-face...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.10,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:39.89,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the special-grade cursed spirit \Nthat's been messing with our idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.20,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.12,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Am I famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:45.04,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:47.77,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you ran with your \Ntail between your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:50.58,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.06,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,You seem worth killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.64,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had any good \Nchances to shine today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:02.05,Italics,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,They said this thing's technique \Nhad something to do with souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:04.56,Italics,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,and not to let its hands touch me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:08.81,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,...so I'll have to settle for \Nexorcising a cowardly bug like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:10.83,Italics,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Recall it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:15.21,Italics,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Recall the essence of cursed energy \Nthat you seized back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.94,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,No control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.68,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hairpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:38.88,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:42.23,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,But in general, that won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:44.85,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from what she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:47.36,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,she must be close to that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:50.71,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drag this woman's corpse
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:54.04,Italics,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,before Yuji Itadori and break his soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:27.17,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Time for a personality test!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:29.88,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Can you more clearly recall \Nthe person you used to love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:31.36,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}or the person you used to hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:33.14,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Results after the title!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.20,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next time, "Right and Wrong, Part 2."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:39.93,Next_Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\blur4}Next Episode\N{\fs30\fscy150}Right and Wrong, Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:39.75,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dwelling on the past means you're an otaku!

